# VOAI Design System Rules

## Brand Tokens
- Only use color tokens from globals.css (#16A34A for brand, var(--bg), var(--fg), etc.)
- Never use raw hex colors except #16A34A, #000000, #FFFFFF
- Typography: San Francisco (SF Pro) for headlines, Epilogue for body text
- Border radius: 12px (md), 16px (lg), 24px (xl)
- Shadow: Only use shadow-card (0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08))

## Code Style
- Use Server Components by default
- Server Actions over Route Handlers
- Prefer editing existing files over creating new ones
- Never create documentation files unless explicitly requested
- No comments unless asked

## Performance & Security
- ISR with revalidate: 3600 for static pages
- CSP headers configured in next.config.ts
- Rate limiting via middleware.ts
- Always use Supabase SSR for auth